過程的機制，並說明牛乳中的鈣離子（Ca²⁺）在此凝膠網絡生成過程中
所扮演之角色。（6 分）', '[]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, FALSE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:12:00+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "bd3df6b0708a", "answer_pdf_sha1": null, "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "114180", "c": "020", "s": "0806", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "甲、申論題部分", "subject": "食品化學", "year": "114", "exam_name": "114年專技人員高等考試建築師、25類科技師(含第二次食品技師)、大地工程技師考試分階段考試(第二階段考試)暨普通考試不動產經紀人、記帳士考...", "original_question_number": "五", "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "food", "db_exam_id": "food-tech"}'::jsonb, NULL),
